text: The Fencer (, ) is a 2015 Finnish Estonian German drama movie directed by Klaus Härö and starring Märt Avandi, Ursula Ratasepp, Liisa Koppel, Lembit Ulfsak, Leida Rammo, Piret Kalda, Kirill Käro. ==Other websites== * Category:2015 drama movies Category:Finnish movies Category:Estonian movies Category:German drama movies
